&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recognized as the No. 1 site trusted by real estate professionals, Realtor.com® has been at the forefront of online real estate for over 25 years, connecting buyers, sellers, and renters with trusted insights and expert guidance to find their perfect home. Through its robust suite of tools, Realtor.com® not only makes a significant impact on the real estate industry at large, but for consumers, navigating the biggest purchase they will make in their life, by providing a user experience that is easy to use, easy to understand, and most of all, easy to make decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us on our mission to empower more people to find their way home by breaking barriers to entry, making the right connections, and building confidence through expert guidance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;141&quot; data-local-id=&quot;9772fa1ddc43&quot;&gt;The Realtor.com® Brand &amp;amp; Creative team is building the AI infrastructure that powers the next generation of consumer and client marketing. Not experimenting. Building — a full creative operating system that spans audience intelligence, brief development, concepting, production, and the performance feedback that makes every campaign smarter than the last.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;496&quot; data-local-id=&quot;779677cf57ef&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;AI Creative Systems Director&lt;/strong&gt; owns that system.&amp;nbsp;You won&#39;t audit, strategize, or pilot. You&#39;ll be embedded from day one — building working AI systems on real deliverables, connecting the intelligence that feeds great briefs to the production that delivers great creative, and continuously raising what&#39;s possible across every role.&amp;nbsp;If your instinct is to ship a working proof-of-concept on a real brief today rather than present a deck about what&#39;s theoretically possible next quarter — this is your role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;989&quot; data-local-id=&quot;908dd9508f52&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1006&quot; data-local-id=&quot;e5cba7057479&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Creative Intelligence Infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt; The connective tissue of the whole system. Audience signals that inform briefs. AI-assisted brief development that accelerates concepting. Performance feedback that makes the next campaign smarter. You design and build the layer that connects every stage of the creative process — so the team makes better decisions faster, whether it&#39;s a brand campaign or high-volume paid social production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1437&quot; data-local-id=&quot;524342eafd96&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Video AI Systems&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with the Motion Design team to identify where AI creates the greatest opportunity in video storytelling and production. Evaluate and standardize the tools that power it. Design the workflow that lets the team produce AI-assisted video at velocity — lo-fi concept video, short-form paid social variants, campaign cutdowns — without sacrificing creative quality. You don&#39;t direct the videos. You build the system that makes directing them faster, smarter, and more scalable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1936&quot; data-local-id=&quot;1dbbaeaea017&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Brief, Research &amp;amp; Concepting&lt;/strong&gt; Build the AI layer that makes strategy and concepting faster and sharper. Audience research synthesized by agents so strategists aren&#39;t spending days on desk research. Competitive signals surfaced automatically. Multi-model concepting workflows that give creative directors more territory to react to in less time. AI compresses the time between brief and conviction

