&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recognized as the No. 1 site trusted by real estate professionals, Realtor.com® has been at the forefront of online real estate for over 25 years, connecting buyers, sellers, and renters with trusted insights and expert guidance to find their perfect home. Through its robust suite of tools, Realtor.com® not only makes a significant impact on the real estate industry at large, but for consumers, navigating the biggest purchase they will make in their life, by providing a user experience that is easy to use, easy to understand, and most of all, easy to make decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us on our mission to empower more people to find their way home by breaking barriers to entry, making the right connections, and building confidence through expert guidance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consumer Success Coordinator&lt;/strong&gt; at&lt;strong&gt; Realtor.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Scottsdale, AZ (Hybrid/In-Office 3 days per week)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a sales coordinating expert? Are you ready to support the full sales cycle from client vetting to confirm a deal? If you want to pursue your professional goals as you help grow an innovative real estate tech company, this work is for you. Join us as our newest Consumer Success Coordinator and help change the world of real estate, one home at a time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Top Reasons to Apply:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Great Pay &amp;amp; Benefits;&amp;nbsp;$21.50/hour + commission, earning potential $56,200/year, with top-tier benefits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Career Growth;&amp;nbsp;Tackle new challenges and advance in an innovative real estate tech company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fun, Dynamic Team;&amp;nbsp;Join a high-energy team, enjoy flexible hours, and make a real impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make outbound calls to identify client&#39;s needs and respond with superior service and resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to understand client&#39;s objectives and challenges and align our services to accomplish their goals via phone, email, and SMS communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle from client vetting to confirm a deal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize our in-house CRM System and work the&amp;nbsp;pipeline of inbound clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track goals, metrics, and performance of the process and regularly provide feedback and make suggestions for improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years&#39; experience in a phone-based customer service role or equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills - no fear of the phone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to a high standard of integrity and working in a team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When faced with new challenges, or tough conversations, failure simply isn&#39;t an option.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Desire to grow your career and tackle new challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to succinctly explain products, answer questions, provide solutions, and negotiate the best deal to maximize profitability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A genuine interest/background in the real estate industry and excited to be part of something that&#39;s going to change the real estate space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated with a desire to work in a dynamic and fast paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate the ability to use strategic selling skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized, independent, resourceful and diligent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent listener, assertive, persistent, and persuasive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scheduling flexibility is required as some shifts require holidays, late evening, or weekend hours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recognized as the No. 1 site trusted by real estate professionals, Realtor.com® has been at the forefront of online real estate for over 25 years, connecting buyers, sellers, and renters with trusted insights and expert guidance to find their perfect home. Through its robust suite of tools, Realtor.com® not only makes a significant impact on the real estate industry at large, but for consumers, navigating the biggest purchase they will make in their life, by providing a user experience that is easy to use, easy to understand, and most of all, easy to make decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us on our mission to empower more people to find their way home by breaking barriers to entry, making the right connections, and building confidence through expert guidance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Care Representative&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;at&lt;strong&gt; Realtor.com&lt;br&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Scottsdale, AZ (Hybrid/3 days in office)&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you driven to excel in a high-performance environment where your efforts create meaningful impact? At Realtor.com, we are seeking a passionate &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Care Representative&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; to join our dynamic team. We operate on a foundation of &quot;Real&quot; values that define our culture of excellence:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Purpose:&lt;/strong&gt; We are united by our mission to help everyone find their home and to support our core customers, real estate agents and brokers, in improving their business outcomes, ensuring every interaction makes a difference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Ambition:&lt;/strong&gt; We strive for continuous growth, challenging ourselves to exceed performance goals and career milestones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Innovation:&lt;/strong&gt; We embrace change and creative problem-solving to improve the software and support experiences we provide.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; We work together as a cohesive unit, supporting one another to deliver world-class service to our real estate professionals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; We take full accountability for our work, handling inquiries with accuracy, empathy, and professional integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are an enthusiastic self-starter ready to thrive in a fast-paced, high-performance environment, we invite you to apply and help us shape the future of real estate support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently hiring FULL-TIME Customer Care Representative (CCR) professionals for our inbound call center! Successful candidates will possess strong skills in providing &lt;strong&gt;world-class customer service &lt;/strong&gt;at all times. Strong interpersonal skills, being a self-starter, and an ability to quickly adapt to change are required in this fast-paced, high-volume inbound customer service center.&amp;nbsp; Let your customer service skills shine as you deliver exceptional service to our customers who are professionals in the real estate industry. While supporting our customers, you will provide prompt, efficient handling of customer inquiries, such as offering insight into our company products, troubleshooting software issues, and addressing billing and general inquiries.&lt;/p&gt;
