&lt;li&gt;This is a high traffic, high velocity application so key skills will involve applying engineering best practices, SEO, page load performance, effective testing strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and optimize our backend services around fetching and processing data efficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and operationalize data pipelines using advanced data architectures deployed on Amazon Web Services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize our developer toolchain to support instant provisioning of new services and infrastructure, fully automate deployment, and minimize development friction&lt;/li&gt;
